messageBody:
--- In junit@yahoogroups.com, barath amarnath <barzenith@y...> wrote:
> Hi All,
> we are executing Junit test cases from ANT script. The
> most of the test cases are passed but few of them
> failed due to the following error message.
>
> Error in executing stored procedure ORA-00942: table
> or view does not exist
> http://mail.yahoo.com

When the datbase is failing, does the problem occur elsewhere? If so
the problem has nothing to do with junit and you should ask in an
oracle forum. If not, you need to determine what is different between
the two clients (failing junit and correct operation elsewhere).
